Source-Makefile: feeds/packages/libs/libnfc/Makefile
Package: libnfc
Version: 1.4.2-1
Depends: +libc +USE_EGLIBC:librt +USE_EGLIBC:libpthread +libusb +pcscd +ccid
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: libs
Category: Libraries
Title: Near Field Communication (NFC) library
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Source: libnfc-1.4.2.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description:   libnfc is a free software library used to handle NFC capable devices.
  It supports the four main NFC modulations:
   * ISO14443-A (NXP MIFARE),
   * ISO14443-B,
   * JIS X 6319-4 (Sony Felica) and
   * Jewel Topaz (Innovision Research & Development).
  And depending on hardware, it supports:
   * Read (RFID @13.56Mhz),
   * Emulation and
   * Peer2Peer mode.  
http://www.libnfc.org
OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
@@

Package: libnfc-bin
