Depends: +libc +USE_EGLIBC:librt +USE_EGLIBC:libpthread +libnfc
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: utils
Category: Utilities
Title: Near Field Communication (NFC) library (binaries)
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Source: libnfc-1.4.2.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description:   libnfc is provided with some useful tools:
   * nfc-list: target listing;
   * nfc-mfclassic: Mifare Classic operations;
   * nfc-mfultralight: Mifare Ultralight operations.
http://www.libnfc.org
OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
@@

